opam-version: "2.0"
synopsis: "Easy to use and user-friendly topological sort"
description: """\
Easy to use and user-friendly topological sort.

Example:
```
Tsort.sort [("foundation", []); ("walls", ["foundation"]); ("roof", ["walls"])]
```"""
